input : string sentence , int n
output : two strings right , left
processing :
find the word most to the left repeated at least n times (right)
find the word most to the right repeate at least n times (left)
if there is only one word repeated at least n times , return right=the word  left = ""
example :
  input : "car x car car for for for x x " , 3
  output : right = x , left = car
